      • authenticate

        public void authenticate(java.lang.String username,
                         java.lang.String password)
        Authenticate user with username and password. The user can set a different host by setting it in Config class
        Parameters:
        username(String) - email of the user
        password(String) - password of the user

      • authenticate

        public void authenticate(java.lang.String host,
                         java.lang.String username,
                         java.lang.String password)
        Authenticate user with username and password. The user can set a different host by setting it in Config class
        Parameters:
        host(String) - URL of the server where graphs are hosted. User can also use this library with self hosted graphs
        username(String) - email of the user
        password(String) - password of the user
